    {
      "instruction": "<p>Reboil a kettle</p><p>Peel and finely chop your <strong>shallot[s]</strong></p><p>Peel and finely chop (or grate) your <strong>garlic</strong></p><p>Return the reserved pan to a medium-high heat with a small knob of <strong>butter</strong></p><p>Once melted, add the <strong>chopped shallot, chopped garlic </strong>and a pinch of<strong> salt</strong> and cook for 2 min or until softened</p>",
